snippet.title: Why Is Switzerland So Expensive?

localized.description:
–Richard Wolff, Professor Emeritus of Economics at the University of Massachusetts, and currently a visiting professor at the New School University in New York City, joins David to discuss evaluating a country’s economy, and the current economy in Switzerland

–On the Bonus Show: Verizon’s “auto share,” Apple’s smart watch, Google partners with a pharmaceutical giant, more…
